      "message": "Patch Set 3: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 5.7/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/10083f0a-33b5-11e1-8da0-5254004bbbd3).  Ran 13 tests.  No failures.",
